{"tid":1693540,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【為星期日正名】啱啱星期日係自發！係自發！各區開花，RE魏書洛陽城巴打個po，商場戰必須打！","createTime":"2019-11-04T16:03:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-06T02:05:10.000Z","uid":110109,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"001589182ac51c46b318a8e174b36aaa1497900c","tid":1693540,"uid":110109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T16:03:20.000Z","msg":"啱啱星期日<br />\n我地有手足比黑警放TG逼迫差少少就冇命依家垂危<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">有單拖面對黑警爆曬缸既將軍澳義士</span></span><br />\n<br />\n但其實星期日好緊要！<br />\n事先其實係<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">冇大型號召過各區開花既，得星期六晚小規模推po（在此感謝手足）</span></span><br />\n<br />\n係沙田手足帶頭、大埔玩足一晚、屯門元朗都出左黎、最尾將軍澳埋齋！<br />\n<br />\n效果係咩？<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">記得星期六我地好灰機比黑警打壓覺得當日接近係白做</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">覺得香港人反抗只係口號</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">港共政府建制派準備開香檳話暴力退潮</span></span><br />\n<br />\n結果呢！<br />\n係自發各區開花！自發呀！<br />\n商場戰上個禮拜誠然都有被捕、有流血<br />\n但係比起喺港島太子大路上面比黑警掃蕩、行人路上面濫捕濫暴發洩&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n黎得再安全一啲<br />\n都唔係港豬已經見慣既事<br />\n既然暫時短期目標我地唔清晰<br />\n我地仲試緊組織三罷、我地等人權法<br />\n我地有迷失，需要儲氣文宣搞下一次大遊行乜柒都好<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">暫時不如shift去商場戰</span></span><br />\n睇下飛天南（升天）巴打既po<br />\n只有堅持先有希望而唔係倒轉<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><br />\n商家佬你想獨善其身？<br />\n港豬你想星期六落apple store玩手機、星期日食元氣？？？<br />\n<br />\n我地要撚到你真點零售寒冬、直到聖誕、直到五大訴求被滿足！<br />\n攬炒呀屌你老母</span></span>"},{"pid":"3aa229fb4b9612dec8d9fb9aaab4a4df56510a7c","tid":1693540,"uid":110109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T16:03:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f49913edf18681575265c05d0329b1154f87e9ce","tid":1693540,"uid":110109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T16:05:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54d7e9c645286f1ad79b403d6e8e27fe46591523","tid":1693540,"uid":110109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T16:05:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f25c1caac122180d862159493439bf2aaa9de9a","tid":1693540,"uid":110109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T16:05:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1200a82c6cb2b7d23e7763b14830f11a6fc47961","tid":1693540,"uid":110109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T16:05:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4446fb509fe55d95b6388d8ebc6a30ef06e954f0","tid":1693540,"uid":217405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T16:06:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6e7a5fec216cf6e01fe893d9770e55dabec4f449","tid":1693540,"uid":110109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T16:06:35.000Z","msg":"仲有太古街坊！<br />\n我地有兩公婆俾人捅腹部<br />\n我地要打落去<br />\n堅持落去"},{"pid":"9e8c249a4005401b41c8e8277f7ca36c2ea2d1e3","tid":1693540,"uid":110109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T16:06:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5232f2f1cee2c09806a533ef947706556214d3f1","tid":1693540,"uid":110109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T16:07:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b6375efb94517139ce650dde9b417df2c8a0af7","tid":1693540,"uid":110109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T16:07:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65ded37dfefdfb56369a5b5f9afd482830ec0043","tid":1693540,"uid":110109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T16:07:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4bae937f25db6c2d0a240d8e55a01d5b9bced9b9","tid":1693540,"uid":110109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T16:07:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77ce64076a340561b5690858cfa1f0c1104c9a26","tid":1693540,"uid":110109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T16:07:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71c2cb61b13ca45e6157bb54085a200857b50ed7","tid":1693540,"uid":51621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T16:10:45.000Z","msg":"商場戰"},{"pid":"fa62fc6eed6d9ffa991f4af9b6f1c63b993965a8","tid":1693540,"uid":110109,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T16:11:07.000Z","msg":"要幫科大手足行埋落去<br />\n要幫好多好多人行落去<br />\n<br />\nSSP被撞腳既女仔<br />\nTST被射眼既女仔<br />\n金鐘被射眼既老師<br />\n荃灣中槍既健仔、被斬腳既手足<br />\n太多太多喇<br />\n一定唔可以休息、一休息就玩完"},{"pid":"20fb11c2a39e7ad98ed344116be1118bd21f084b","tid":1693540,"uid":69503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T16:11:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f21a39c5f5183cf284e7362adacb6f452da178ab","tid":1693540,"uid":110109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T16:12:37.000Z","msg":"大埔被劏肚既男仔<br />\n上水被逼跳橋既男仔<br />\n觀塘都有個差啲被射盲<br />\n<br />\n差唔多區區都有喇<br />\n你嗰區仲有冇原因唔出黎 繼續休息？？"},{"pid":"8153c486d280b80808f602932d7bf40cb04b463e","tid":1693540,"uid":110109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T16:13:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"58ce7e4033a15dd1570aa08bce1b4d74b0aff972","tid":1693540,"uid":110109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T16:13:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7ff7848e10003c7800e2e65d10fdbbb5cde2e292","tid":1693540,"uid":110109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"r